Package: cryptroot-package
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Richard Oliver <richard.oliver@raspberrypi.com>
Depends: cryptsetup-bin, libgcc-s1, cryptkey-fetch-otp
Recommends: cryptkey-rpifwcrypto
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: Init script and systemd service for LUKS-encrypted root
 Unlocks the root partition using a key from cryptkey-rpifwcrypto
 (preferred) or cryptkey-fetch-otp (fallback), mounts the root and boot
 partitions, and pivots into the real root using systemctl switch-root.
